<h2 class="bold font-l">Sweet Dreams</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Quicksilver's bullet time returns in epic fashion, as he uses it to evacuate the entirety of the X-Mansion, to the tune of Sweet Dreams. </p>
<p class='example_row'>Example of:<br><a href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/BulletTime" class='trope-example-link'>Bullet Time</a></p>
</div>
</div>
